subtitle: in the middle of the Endless expanse of
the Pacific Ocean in Micronesia there
lies a megalithic site as inexplicable
and mysterious as any on earth a site
which has been a breeding ground of
Legends and secrets for centuries and
yet despite its status as one of the
most enigmatic and unique ancient sites
in the world most people have probably
never heard the name Nan madal yet
despite its remote location and
inhospitable terrain pipe is home to the
remains of megalithic architecture on an
unparalleled scale in
Micronesia in the shallow Waters off its
eastern shore stands an unfathomable
Stone complex 92 artificial eyelets
built on top of a coral reef over an
area a mile long all linked by an
elaborate network of ston lined canals
